# Vite automatically loads this file for `vite build` (mode "production").
# Unlike .env.local, this is committed — VITE_API_URL isn't a secret, and
# baking it in here means the server never needs a manual shell export
# before building (which is easy to forget, and was the actual cause of
# a whole afternoon of "registration doesn't save" debugging).
VITE_API_URL=https://api.sturdylifer.com/api
